-- Palestinian Advisory Board Tells Abbas to Suspend Peace Talks With Israel
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   F e r z i g e r
-- 2010-10-02T13:13:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-02/palestinian-advisory-board-tells-abbas-to-suspend-peace-talks-with-israel.html
A group advising Palestinian
Authority President Mahmoud Abbas recommended that he stop
Middle East peace talks because of Israel’s renewed construction
in West Bank settlements. Abbas spokesman Nabil Abu Rudeineh
announced the decision after the Palestine Liberation
Organization’s Executive Committee met today in the West Bank
city of Ramallah.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Ferziger at 
 jferziger@bloomberg.net  